    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been reviewed. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain not-assessed due to epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Despite achieved levels falling below required levels on multiple factors, the assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile pending supplementary evidence. No context of use has been defined in this package.",
